<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>비즈니스 메인 페이지</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/1.main.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <!-- <h1 class="logo">ESS-M.S</h1>ESS Monitoring system -->
            <h1 class="logo" onclick="location.href='1.main.html'" style="cursor:pointer;">ESS-M.S</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                <li><a href="1.main.html">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="3.serviceInfo.html">서비스 소개</a></li>
                <li><a href="2.contact.html">문의게시판</a></li>
                <li id="auth-menu">
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="login-btn" onclick="openLoginWindow()">로그인</a>
                </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" onclick="location.href='3.serviceInfo.html';" style="cursor:pointer;">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h2>환경과 사회를 위한 최상의 선택</h2>
            <p>우리 아이와 함께할 미래를 위해 고민합니다.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

<!-- 날씨 섹션, 예시용 실시간 X -->
<section class="weather-section container">
    <div class="weather-title">
        <h3>☀️ 전국 주요 지역 날씨</h3>
        <p>실시간 기상 상황을 확인하세요.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="weather-grid">
        <div class="weather-item">
            <span class="city">서울</span>
            <span class="icon">☀️</span>
            <span class="temp">12°C</span>
        </div>
        <div class="weather-item">
            <span class="city">부산</span>
            <span class="icon">☁️</span>
            <span class="temp">15°C</span>
        </div>
        <div class="weather-item">
            <span class="city">대구</span>
            <span class="icon">☀️</span>
            <span class="temp">14°C</span>
        </div>
        <div class="weather-item">
            <span class="city">광주</span>
            <span class="icon">⛅</span>
            <span class="temp">13°C</span>
        </div>
        <div class="weather-item">
            <span class="city">제주</span>
            <span class="icon">🌧️</span>
            <span class="temp">18°C</span>
        </div>
</section>
    <section class="services container">
        <div class="service-card" onclick="location.href='2.contact.html'" style="cursor:pointer;">
            <h3>문의 게시판</h3>
            <p>여러가지 문의 사항을 접수 합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card bg-info" onclick="location.href='7.newsupdate.html'" style="cursor:pointer;">
            <h3>ESS 최신 정보</h3>
            <p>ESS 관련 정보를 제공합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card" onclick="goToMonitoring()" style="cursor: pointer;">
            <h3>발전량 확인 하러 가기</h3>
            <p>로그인 후 확인 가능합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 발전량 확인하러 가기 눌렀을때 로그인 상태 확인 -->
            <script src="js/1.main.js"></script>
    </section>

    <section class="board container">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <h3 style="margin: 0;">ESS 최신 정보</h3>
        <a href="7.newsupdate.html" style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; text-decoration: none;">더보기 +</a>
    </div>
    
    <table class="board-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 80px;">번호</th>
                <th>제목</th>
                <th style="width: 120px;">날짜</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>4</td>
                <td class="txt-left">
                    <a href="8.news_view.html?id=4" class="board-link">[기술] 차세대 배터리 매니지먼트 시스템(BMS) 효율 측정 결과</a>
                </td>
                <td>2024.03.20</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>3</td>
                <td class="txt-left">
                    <a href="8.news_view.html?id=3" class="board-link">[공지] ESS-M.S 모니터링 시스템 정기 점검 안내 (3/25)</a>
                </td>
                <td>2024.03.18</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</section>

    <!-- 로그인 창 열기 스크립트 -->
    <script>
        function openLoginWindow() {
            window.open('4.login copy.html', 'login', 'width=500,height=600,top=100,left=100');
        }
    </script>

    <!-- 로그인 체크기능 -->
<script src="js/1.main.js"></script>




<!-- 페이지 맨 아래 회사 정보, 주소, 연락처 공간 -->
    <footer>
    <div class="container footer-content">
        <div class="footer-info">
            <h2 class="footer-logo">ESS-M.S</h2>
            <p>스마트 에너지 모니터링 시스템 전문 기업</p>
            <address>
                부산광역시 범내골 kh 학원 <br>
                대표전화: 051-123-4567 | 이메일: info@ess-ms.com
            </address>
            <p class="copyright">&copy; 2026 ESS-Monitoring System. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-links">
            <h4>Quick Links</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="1.main.html">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="3.serviceInfo.html">서비스 소개</a></li>
                <li><a href="2.contact.html">문의게시판</a></li>
                <li><a href="7.newsupdate.html">최신 정보</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-sns">
            <h4>Follow Us</h4>
            <div class="sns-icons">
                <span>Blog</span>
                <span>LinkedIn</span>
                <span>Youtube</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
